{"tid":775371,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［另類］被困深山兩個月","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T09:09:14.000Z","uid":130268,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ee266ffb26bb587ba31c3d31f5816d4b6b68ef","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"&quot;六月開始Field trip。頭兩個禮拜落torridon,然後個半月自己揀地方,有無問題?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;請問佔幾多分？&quot;<br />\n&ldquo;頭兩個禮拜degree無分,然後個半月既project佔final degree 30%同埋係你desertation既一部份。仲有無問題?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n無分點解我要去？<br />\n&ldquo;可唔可以唔去？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;唔去你repeat year3啦&rdquo;<br />\n屌，又話無分？仆你個街,呃尻我<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;學費包唔包架？&quot;<br />\n&quot;唔包,三餐都唔包。唔好詐詐帝帝,記得準時鎊水呀!&quot;<br />\n仗義半從屠狗輩；負心多是讀書人。<br />\n所謂有教無類,悔人好卷,春風化雨全部都係謊話,最關心既不過係錢。以前不嬲免費架,做乜撚野今年field trip要比錢呀？我有交學費架柒頭,依家仲要屈我比錢！果然係大學之道,明明明屈。<br />\n<br />\n究竟前世做錯乜,搞到讀地質？<br />\n<br />\nAny肥,我就係咁被困深山60日"},{"pid":"d87b7a1321e6414960efd6774dc3453c4b4ace49","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"Torridon,isles of skye 對岸，位於蘇格蘭高地。點解要去torridon?<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知。我淨係知打後兩個禮拜要六點起身十點訓,行7個鐘山餵蚊,返黎夜晚要交assigment,wifi 淨係load到144p,同人爭沖涼同埋要煮三餐非常痛苦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/46iLRX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F46iLRX.jpg&h=ab224d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/8JZb3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F8JZb3I.jpg&h=0bcd82ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/2NwpXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F2NwpXx.jpg&h=cb96006d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/n4R3Qp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2Fn4R3Qp.jpg&h=6bdbd5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/64qYwD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F64qYwD.jpg&h=1185ea77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山明水秀<br />\n風景秀麗"},{"pid":"2f37f3ab313baf4709efc6519e148735675156aa","tid":775371,"uid":33777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6b821479dfac53ee5eaf357f554c3790b8b421a3","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"呢度風光明媚,一片片綠幽幽既山林盡收眼底，實在教人心爌神怡。奈何工務繁忙,良辰美景亦無暇細心恩賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/2C1dmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F2C1dmt.jpg&h=7688636f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/GbQqmI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FGbQqmI.jpg&h=dd5ca157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/SxUEc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FSxUEc0.jpg&h=e5d1686f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/qsV7Jm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FqsV7Jm.jpg&h=cc4ed394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返工慘但有糧出。屌喇星,今次真係貼錢買難受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9aa0b66620fd318cd42011866bd7b0f4f49e966","tid":775371,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b821479dfac53ee5eaf357f554c3790b8b421a3","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"呢度風光明媚,一片片綠幽幽既山林盡收眼底，實在教人心爌神怡。奈何工務繁忙,良辰美景亦無暇細心恩賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/2C1dmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https