mbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FGbQqmI.jpg&h=dd5ca157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/SxUEc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FSxUEc0.jpg&h=e5d1686f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/qsV7Jm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FqsV7Jm.jpg&h=cc4ed394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返工慘但有糧出。屌喇星,今次真係貼錢買難受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"讀乜科？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"地質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64d2991e9c7fe926c371f314f6fba7c835196a9","tid":775371,"uid":15087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"風景咁靚咪好好享受lor"},{"pid":"e6e719d495421ef4eb0d4601d3ed109470038f30","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/142158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F142158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=11ef5437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/142201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F142201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=55f8de02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n親親大自然,玩弄小動物"},{"pid":"8dffa0854ff97f98fb246207e17ad3b43473b793","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"說時遲那時快,咁就過左兩個禮拜。老實講無乜感想,因為真係身心疲累,精神不濟。咁搞法遲早荷爾蒙失調,内汾泌失敗。<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家應該從文字中感受到我強烈無比既怨恨。再繼續怨天怨地,憤世嫉俗,同埋成日off topic大家就扭台架喇。言歸正傳,黎緊六個禮拜去西班牙！"},{"pid":"0a371952efc09955b2d9c3308105f19c99747650","tid":775371,"uid":75432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"6月去左isle of skye <br />\n租左coupe 去皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1985c70ac69c54f4528cf2c0b7079e9eb6107515","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a371952efc09955b2d9c3308105f19c99747650","tid":775371,"uid":75432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"6月去左isle of skye <br />\n租左coupe 去皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"我要做野架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過skye 風景超靚"},{"pid":"d1bb40ac2e82dda2b1c42d3607569520f3312858","tid":775371,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇 Narcos"},{"pid":"9c1f95aaff5e2a3d358c9cd929129ffabf8f63a1","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"今次去嘅係 aragon 嘅aliaga。呢度人煙罕至,坐車四粒鐘,轉兩次車先到。一三五先有車,一日一班,死未？可以話係西班牙嘅沙頭角,又或者係七十年代既新界,着草三五七年都無人知。<br />\n<br />\n華倫西亞沿路見到嘅西班妹可謂一流,個個玲瓏浮突,婀娜多姿。西班牙人普遍浪漫不羈,熱情奔放。情到濃時就打個茄倫慶祝下,攬錫摸巢可謂等閑視之,用行動表示愛與激情。呢種精神十分值得大家學習。因為時間有限,所以就純文字討論先, 唔好大力屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/UrLvGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FUrLvGY.jpg&h=d21232e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/hQJjMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FhQJjMN.jpg&h=cb9faf32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/cyuNHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FcyuNHC.jpg&h=1eddf179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/P0mcjW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FP0mcjW.jpg&h=f3c4c5e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/BHOYk4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FBHOYk4.jpg&h=ede7b684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/BcapHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FBcapHf.jpg&h=744ec91f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由Valencia坐火車去teruel,teruel撘巴士去aliaga<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提,火車站隔離係鬥牛場<br />\n可惜聽日晨早流流就要走喇,要隱居深山"},{"pid":"6fe980b4f4580f3dde3865e5bfc662bb4d4d45e7","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c1f95aaff5e2a3d358c9cd929129ffabf8f63a1","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"今次去嘅係 aragon 嘅aliaga。呢度人煙罕至,坐車四粒鐘,轉兩次車先到。一三五先有車,一日一班,死未？可以話係西班牙嘅沙頭角,又或者係七十年代既新界,着草三五七年都無人知。<br />\n<br />\n華倫西亞沿路見到嘅西班妹可謂一流,個個玲瓏浮突,婀娜多姿。西班牙人普遍浪漫不羈,熱情奔放。情到濃時就打個茄倫慶祝下,攬錫摸巢可謂等閑視之,用行動表示愛與激情。呢種精神十分值得大家學習。因為時間有限,所以就純文字討論先, 唔好大力屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/UrLvGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FUrLvGY.jpg&h=d21232e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/hQJjMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FhQJjMN.jpg&h=cb9faf32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/cyuNHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A