rc=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/2C1dmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F2C1dmt.jpg&h=7688636f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/GbQqmI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FGbQqmI.jpg&h=dd5ca157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/SxUEc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FSxUEc0.jpg&h=e5d1686f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/17/qsV7Jm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2FqsV7Jm.jpg&h=cc4ed394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返工慘但有糧出。屌喇星,今次真係貼錢買難受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"讀乜科？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"地質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b526051c031596056040e1e3e1862c5374bc75a2","tid":775371,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"有冇野外露出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cb488cd5fb72dcccc856839d5868b9f488e74a","tid":775371,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e57b15e8a710627a50e406ad5a886f663cd0b5c","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1bb40ac2e82dda2b1c42d3607569520f3312858","tid":775371,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇 Narcos"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:30:52.000Z","msg":"有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以先改個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:59.000Z","msg":"第三季最好睇<br />\n唔知有冇第4季呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, d 相好靚"},{"pid":"5986d65e0b35c9c7debdf09e76c006dd1c43cdea","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"Teruel 呢個地方唔敢講佢有咩特別之處,因為只係嚟咗個半鐘,主要都係嚟等巴士 。<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/is9NjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2Fis9NjE.jpg&h=788f57b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/qSTkiU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FqSTkiU.jpg&h=f9b8e7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/qCE4fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FqCE4fb.jpg&h=82765939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/Asl07f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FAsl07f.jpg&h=847fc8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/TY9Zub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FTY9Zub.jpg&h=64532e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e82c6b2afd22c5379c8fb938b0bad819f25c7da2","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"係度問路無google map真係慘撚過死。因為大部分人都唔識講英文,完全係雞同鴨講。偏偏佢哋又好鍾意碟碟不休咁同你用西班牙文溝通,以為講多兩句你就會明,真係吹脹。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/UQ7Dn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FUQ7Dn8.jpg&h=3eab2885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個午餐真扺屌,一盒風乾火腿加個咁嘅沙律加埋都唔&euro;3。喺香港如果畀我老母知道我一餐食佢十二塊風乾火腿,肯定雙手運勁,一巴打撚死我都似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/GtzSaq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FGtzSaq.jpg&h=5ba74f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然人有三急，衝入廁所。屌你老味無尿兜嘅？仆街唔小心入咗女廁添。好彩冇人係入面, 如果唔係跳落尼羅河都洗唔清！話唔定啲女人喺入面傾緊點樣去殺啲男人呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/143513_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F143513_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d826dab2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c034fa4103648dba6a39970fa07067f83661599","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"撘車去aliaga。坐到某個點,個司機突然間叫我落車。賣飛果陣原全無提過要轉車。佢不停咁講西班牙文,亦完全唔理會我明唔明白。我地彷彿係一對分緊手既情侶,大家自說自話,絲毫沒有半點溝通。<br />\n<br />\n是否不甘心 首先給撇下,<br />\n換了你是我你忍得到嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/jgUX1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FjgUX1v.jpg&h=4160939c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荒山野嶺尻企,同我既前途一樣,十分之迷惘。"},{"pid":"8c9b795a5873b84fdc052ebe59c1b46154e97140","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"三個字之後有架車。人類總是要犯重複的錯誤,個司機走埋黎講左一堆西班牙文。<br />\n其實我唔明你繼續講又有咩意思？為繼續而繼續,沒有好處還是我。<br />\n<br />\n我只好苦笑,因為根本唔知佢噏乜尻,唯有用手指指住張車飛個目的地,手語溝通。佢點頭,咁我唯有當你係。正如拖住女仔隻手,佢唔縮我繼續。"},{"pid":"5e44eefa2f633364ad1670bdb79ff9e067ba334f","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"坐坐下,咦,仆你個街掉頭既喂!我屌你老母呀!你唔撚係玩尻我呀嘛,睇錯左?！突然間被司機嚇到九叔,如坐針氈,頓時驚慌失措。淡定如我亦少不忘手忙腳亂,再度用手指指撚住張車飛。佢面色一沉,又嗡一段西班牙文,我心裡喑叫不妙。<br />\n<br />\n落錯車　如離開了幸福的高速路<br />\n誰又保證我明天將更好？<br />\n<br />\n莫非佢見架車無人,諗住車我第二度,劏我死牛？我面如死灰,荒山野嶺簡直係任人擺佈!<br />\n錢唔係問題,問題係冇錢。肉隨針板上,身無分文既我依家可以點？<br />\n<br />\n 過咗一陣,有個初中嘅妹妹上車，我急忙請佢做翻譯。原來佢話架車係會再調返轉頭出發返去目的地。情急之下我竟然錯怪好人,小人之心度君子之腹,實在慚愧 。司機大佬,唔好意思！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/144042_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F144042_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2e8855fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"049a6e15c59e1a7206bc82ffbc3a7fd7160d8652","tid":775371,"uid":89316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"ea0acd4bde82fa33343705def3c2600823bf00d9","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/UJSL36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FUJSL36.jpg&h=266c702a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曖曖遠人村，依依墟里煙。狗吠深巷中，雞鳴桑樹顛。"},{"pid":"66bdc74bc4871e76286a3c5b3c1af587a59d59e0","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"有驚無險又到三點,終於去到hostel 。雖然從來冇嚟過呢度,但係就畀到我好親切嘅感覺。 一入到去就聞到寵物店嗰浸除,十足十細個行旺角金魚街。呢度老細愛心爆棚,好鐘意動物。飛禽走獸,包羅萬有;狗,雞,鴨,金魚,鸚鵡 ,兔仔,龜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/MHsQpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FMHsQpW.jpg&h=8bc1816a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/ye5j0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2Fye5j0b.jpg&h=77ce28b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/kcFCqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FkcFCqr.jpg&h=2d72a44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/gS62jD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FgS62jD.jpg&h=297f11b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/MHsQpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F