\n<br />\noff topic<br />\n<br />\n究竟我係做乜尻？<br />\n1.行山<br />\n2搵石,認石<br />\n3睇下有無地質結構<br />\n4量度角度同緯度,gps<br />\n5劃落地圖度,寫筆記<br />\n6總結,解釋發生咩事<br />\n周而復之,重復六個禮拜<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/wYSuvC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FwYSuvC.jpg&h=6a9bc1d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c3edb6e5afdeedef8bb947e590edf20d45209d4","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"西班牙烏蠅<br />\n呢度d烏蠅多到痴撚線,間直係無處不在。佢地唔咬人不過成日煩q住你,好似d借錢電話咁。奈何數目驚人,殺之不盡,極為苦惱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/rUCQDB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FrUCQDB.jpg&h=5693b0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話唔定食左有助催情<br />\n不過依家我連丁都無得打,咁你地仆街啦！<br />\n一手打死兩隻,佢算執到喇,石榴花下死，做鬼也風流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/eDjZT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FeDjZT1.jpg&h=83742f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬人坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80413bb8ff25d8e1478de6e9311a21cc33f5d1b3","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"To des Fuego Fiesta<br />\n今晚有慶典,我同衛斯理一樣,性喜多管閒事。一於落街睇下。<br />\n半夜三更究竟做乜呢？點解又有欄既呢？<br />\n令我心裡既謎,謎上加謎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/unFLct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FunFLct.jpg&h=486e3737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/9BmQkp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F9BmQkp.jpg&h=3a1d2737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;企入d啦就開波喇。Please stand behind the yellow line 嘟嘟嘟嘟~&rdquo;(咁上下啦）一個當地人同我噏左一段野,示意我企入欄入面。<br />\n<br />\n月圓之夜,紫禁之巔<br />\n一劍西來,天外飛仙？"},{"pid":"58fea148c9e7181df5c7001337da81b88c9cc7f7","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"非也非也,原來今晚係玩鬥牛呀喂！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/pUirAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FpUirAT.jpg&h=06d517c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朦朧是黑色午夜 深不見底~<br />\n所以當地人會係牛角綁上火把,等大家睇到隻牛。隻牛同我當年既朋友阿力一樣,不斷被人挑釁。當地人會向隻牛叫囂,攻擊隻牛,係隻牛面前左穿右插,引隻牛撞向自己欄杆,引以為榮,以此為樂。如果有人成功避開攻擊,大家會歡呼喝彩,以示鼓厲。<br />\n<br />\n生命誠可貴,玩命更實際。作為一名不負責任連登仔,機會千載難逢,我衝左出去。吹咩？面對死亡,我唔害怕。馬車精神,累己累人！<br />\n<br />\n講下啫,one piece仲未畫完,我份保險有排都末扲得返本金,仲唔可以死住。其實我係隻牛後面衝出去,唔算危險,所以我係淆底獸。當然隻牛u turn就另當别論。大家千祈唔好學,得閒唔好入屯門挑釁d牛。"},{"pid":"13268680a630e759c9995e8b4bd4d1ce9659e07b","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"十足十芒亨咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/PvS3aM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FPvS3aM.jpg&h=80bc829f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/A1RU2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FA1RU2u.jpg&h=ad563d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/bqfxvC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FbqfxvC.jpg&h=714d15f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，暴衝<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/pzeoKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FpzeoKX.jpg&h=76bb5400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/Hht0EL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FHht0EL.jpg&h=dcb63bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街,企係隔離個師奶仲癲,踢完隻牛又扯牛尾,慌死佢唔撞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d99b3288901a55bf73c9db020715d6e6ac52fac","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"師奶補圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/151452_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F151452_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6a0aa484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baf828206306b5e47215197e5dafeccb9de86faf","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"「阿根？」唔係雲根,亦都唔係樹根,係我中學同班同學摩根。可能我留左唏噓嘅鬚根,令佢遲疑左幾秒。但係好似我啲咁出色嘅男人,無論嚮咩地方,都好似漆黑中嘅螢火蟲一樣,咁鮮明,咁出眾！大家都相當驚訝,估唔到茫茫人海,竟然係荒山野嶺既鬥牛場偶遇,可謂他鄉遇故知！中學畢業之後大家各奔前程,浪跡天涯,再無見過面。仲以為呢世再無機會見到25g school既校友,真係造化弄人！之後幾個禮拜大家亦都有約出黎睇世界杯,淺酌兩杯,憶述當年荒唐事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/151534_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F151534_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=408c2d9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b98e638ce73bac1f32b4c5dab3250f01e0381cf","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"又Offtopic, 無圖<br />\n介紹下d室友先,全部英國/蘇格蘭人,化名無圖。看倌自行想像,請勿打擾家母。<br />\n<br />\n茄林<br />\n心思細膩,計劃周詳,自攜女友可見一班。負責幫大家訂hostel,拎地圖。後來同條女調房,唔使野戰,顧及他人感受,係一名好男人。<br />\n阿sa<br />\n茄林條女,濃妝豔抹,身在郊野亦不忘化粧，聲如其人,極之煩膠。亦係一名女權分子/西,發表過主流媒體或電影不應該鼓吹大隻六舊腹肌之偉/柒論。<br />\n沙律<br />\n性格爽朗直接,鍾意床上面食零食,貫藉格拉斯哥。平時講野無口音,但一激動/興奮會變做格拉斯哥口音,十分有趣。<br />\n路蘭<br />\n俗語有云:「好狗唔蘭路,路蘭唔狗好」。然而此路蘭正正相反,為人友善樂天,係不可多得既好室友。同沙律份屬友好。<br />\n施仁<br />\n身形高佻,全身有毛。但為人同外觀相反,生性內向斯文,係憂鬱小生。可謂&ldquo;冠蓋滿京華,施仁獨憔悴&rdquo;。做左一個禮拜覺得太難劈砲唔撈,返左英國。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/152011_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F152011_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=daebc6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/152010_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F152010_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=32fc5668&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abe824880d64cb4cb5300d6948b4206597890b78","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"某日早晨,食緊早餐之際突然見到一名西域女子。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;做唔做？&rdquo;<br />\n做帛金？比德仔老豆？<br />\n&ldquo;做訪問？&quot;<br />\n屌你正呀喂！名揚天下,威震四海！原來佢係當地電台記者,黎hostel訪問。做,一定做！老夫定必知無不言，言無不盡！<br />\n<br />\n可惜佢英文水平有限,三個字問左三條問題。阿sa仲正,有得開咪添！如果比我做我一定用廣東話答,成為史上第一位香港人嘉賓。再將佢個節目改名做&ldquo; 大哥講話你要聽&rdquo;,肯定會光宗耀祖,流芳百世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/O8xvK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2FO8xvK5.jpg&h=7fddd3f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/11/8UtMhN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F8UtMhN.jpg&h=dee81c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有圖,立此為証<br />\n大家幫下手,like下呢個post。滿足下我既虛勞心,齊心合力幫我打個飛機,証明老夫深受萬民景仰！"},{"pid":"f018d3a372057f3b41dd7b86b975381f04e67be7","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"其實山入面與世隔絕,悶到出汁。聽聞有人見到毒蛇,蝎子,野豬。慶幸我一隻都見唔到,亦都無乜驚天地泣鬼神既故事。不過如果你問我呢度有咩回憶,除左個晚既星空,我諗唔到有更值得留戀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/152444_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F152444_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ab325856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n友人攝<br />\n<br />\n自問曾經　憧憬　留低此地看星<br />\n無奈我　未得到被邀請~~"},{"pid":"fa3c63d0643c065ddebb1a343794533a9e8d82bb","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"失眠,係我唯一既寫作動力,因為訓唔着先有靈感落筆。最近睡眠充足,精神飽滿,亦無再動筆,所以最後一篇「西班牙油尖旺:華倫西亞」暫時從缺。<br />\n<br />\n聽落去有d離譜,但沙中綫咁多人都接受得到,所以篇文爛尾都唔算太過份。如果有一日又失眠或者有人想睇,咁就擇日再寫。<br />\n<br />\n末完待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcbf0555d6b45669c78390bbdeece0dcd480387","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64d2991e9c7fe926c371f314f6fba7c835196a9","tid":775371,"uid":15087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"風景咁靚咪好好享受lor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"風景靚又咪係要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdaa328e6bb5f0d8e3679ac417493b1e1c010aa","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52f7dab8e4bef4b2f644c6961b0288ea58ffbe08","tid":775371,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8421015760996cbcef32d9f404cf82720249e46f","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9aa0b66620fd318cd42011866bd7b0f4f49e966","tid":775371,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"讀乜科？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"地質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"一念之差讀左呢科"},{"pid":"384927b8d8c88f721a4919a9afb87b86c64a5f71","tid":775371,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b526051c031596056040e1e3e1862c5374bc75a2","tid":775371,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"有冇野外露出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci